DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2014}, 'Dates Optimized'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Canada",
			"United States of America",
			"Mexico"}, 'financials'[Country])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
		TREATAS({"High"}, 'financials'[Discount Band])

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
		__DS0FilterTable,
		__DS0FilterTable2,
		__DS0FilterTable3,
		"DumpFilters", IGNORE('Model_Measures'[DumpFilters])
	)

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2014}, 'Dates Optimized'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Canada",
			"United States of America",
			"Mexico"}, 'financials'[Country])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
		TREATAS({"High"}, 'financials'[Discount Band])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Dates Optimized'[Date],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			__DS0FilterTable3,
			"Sales", 'Model_Measures'[Sales],
			"Max_Sales_Optimized", 'Model_Measures'[Max Sales Optimized],
			"Min_Sales_Optimized", 'Model_Measures'[Min Sales Optimized]
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'Dates Optimized'[Date],
			[Sales],
			[Max_Sales_Optimized],
			[Min_Sales_Optimized],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'Dates Optimized'[Date]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2014}, 'Dates Optimized'[Year])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable2 = 
		TREATAS({"Canada",
			"United States of America",
			"Mexico"}, 'financials'[Country])

	VAR __DS0FilterTable3 = 
		TREATAS({"High"}, 'financials'[Discount Band])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'financials'[Segment],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__DS0FilterTable2,
			__DS0FilterTable3,
			"Sales", 'Model_Measures'[Sales],
			"CountSegment", IGNORE(CALCULATE(COUNTA('financials'[Segment])))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Sales], 0, 'financials'[Segment], 1)

EVALUATE
	GROUPBY(
		__DS0Core,
		"MinCountSegment", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [CountSegment]),
		"MaxCountSegment", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [CountSegment])
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Sales] DESC, 'financials'[Segment]
